847
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:48,000
The Acolyte of Chayula can exchange their mastery of spirit for darkness,

848
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:51,000
a resource that can be utilized to both absorb and deal damage.

849
00:39:51,000 --> 00:40:00,000
The Shroud of Darkness will protect you from all damage incoming, but if you take grasp of the Void, you will deal extra chaos damage from all the darkness you have.

