866
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:42,000
Ascension in Path of Exile 2 requires completion of one of the Great Trials, which you'll find as you progress through the campaign.

867
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:46,000
Each one is associated with one of the major cultures of Rhaeclast.

868
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:55,000
