871
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:16,000
To enter, a warrior of the Marraketh must prove their worth by trapping the soul of a Djinn in a coin, and you are no different.

872
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:23,000
Once you have earned your coin, it may be placed in the Relic Altar to begin the Trial.

873
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:34,000
In the Trial of the Sekimas, each room has its own challenges to overcome.

874
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:39,000
