888
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:51,000
Deadly traps, waves of monsters, and strange artefacts will test your honour.

889
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:57,000
As you progress, you will be able to gain boons from the Djinn, which will help you on your journey.

890
00:43:57,000 --> 00:44:03,000
For example, the Sekimer's Cloak will revive you once if you die, giving you a second shot at a run.

891
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:11,000
