892
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:15,000
Trading it with the Djinn will allow you to receive many benefits.

893
00:44:16,000 --> 00:44:19,000
You can recover honour, gain additional boons, or remove afflictions.

894
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:25,000
At the end of the floor, you will find a powerful boss which will truly test your limitations.

895
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:28,000
In order to ascend, you will need to defeat him.

896
