00:48:21,000 --> 00:48:24,000
So far we've only been showing you footage from the campaign,

952
00:48:24,000 --> 00:48:28,000
but some people would argue that the Endgame is where the game truly begins.

953
00:48:28,000 --> 00:48:32,000
Something that happens almost every time a new action RPG launches is people saying,

954
00:48:32,000 --> 00:48:34,000
there isn't enough Endgame content.

955
00:48:34,000 --> 00:48:37,000
Well, we want to make sure that in PoE 2 people don't feel that way,

956
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:41,000
and we actually only changed our development priority for this recently.

957
00:48:41,000 --> 00:48:46,000
