969
00:49:35,000 --> 00:49:38,000
we've added a second difficulty level called Cruel,

970
00:49:38,000 --> 00:49:43,000
where you repeat the campaign with all the monsters and bosses leveled up, and of course new rewards.

971
00:49:43,000 --> 00:49:46,000
You can kind of think of it as like a new game plus.

972
00:49:46,000 --> 00:49:50,000
It's also a lot faster to get through the content the second time as your clear speed increases.

973
00:49:50,000 --> 00:49:54,000
That will take you to around level 65, where the Endgame begins.

