you will also get a series of hideout statues.

1277
01:15:02,000 --> 01:15:05,000
This pack contains the statue of Hillock.

1278
01:15:05,000 --> 01:15:11,000
For Path of Exile 1's closed beta, each pack contained a true New Zealand icon, the Kiwi.

1279
01:15:11,000 --> 01:15:16,000
Following this tradition, all packs in this series will also contain a new themed Kiwi pet.

1280
01:15:16,000 --> 01:15:20,000
The pet will loyally follow you into battle, but run away at the first sign of trouble.

1281
01:15:21,000 --> 01:15:25,000
Become the ruler of the desert with the King of the Farad'n supporter pack.

1282
01:15:26,000 --> 01:15:29,000
