1283
01:15:30,000 --> 01:15:33,000
The body armour will allow you to glide along the ground with ancient sand magic.

1284
01:15:34,000 --> 01:15:38,000
Now each armour set comes with body armour, boots, gloves and helmet.

1285
01:15:38,000 --> 01:15:40,000
But the boots are covered in sand.

1286
01:15:40,000 --> 01:15:43,000
If you'd prefer to show them off, you can turn the gliding off if you want.

1287
01:15:46,000 --> 01:15:51,000
The accompanying back attachment equips you with two powerful pillars that can control and manipulate lightning.

1288
01:15:52,000 --> 01:15:55,000
They will periodically release their energy in a powerful blast while in town,

1289
01:15:56,000 --> 01:15:59,000
and hover in a circle around you, arcing lightning between them forming a barrier of energy.

