Replace the appearance of any bow with the Farad'n's Glory skin.

1291
01:16:04,000 --> 01:16:08,000
Or replace the appearance of a spear with the Tyranny's End spear skin.

1292
01:16:09,000 --> 01:16:13,000
This spear skin can be applied to staves and war staves in Path of Exile 1.

1293
01:16:14,000 --> 01:16:24,000
If you want to truly show your worth as a King of the Farad'n, then you definitely need your trusty, moving entire city fortress known as the Dreadnaught to travel across the Vasteri plains.

1294
01:16:25,000 --> 01:16:29,000
In Path of Exile you can decorate your hideout however you like, and it's no exception here.

1295
01:16:29,000 --> 01:16:34,000
It comes with a variety of thematic elements to use, or use decorations from elsewhere in the game.

1296
01:16:35,000 --> 01:16:38,000
Additionally, you will get the Deshret's Blessing level up effect.

1297
01:16:39,000 --> 01:16:43,000
The King of the Farad'n Kiwi pet.

1298
01:16:44,000 --> 01:16:49,000
And last but not least, a statue depicting the Vile Oversoul from Path of Exile 1.

1299
