The Thaumaturge of the Vile supporter pack features an armour set and back attachment themed around the Vile and their pursuit of science and progress.

1301
01:17:08,000 --> 01:17:16,000
You can find the Soulcore weapon effect in this pack, which causes Thaumaturgic energy harnessed from Sacrifice to spill from your weapon.

1302
01:17:17,000 --> 01:17:20,000
This pack also contains Dooyani's Idol.

1303
