01:23:05,000 --> 01:23:21,000
To the post-show discussion and Q&A. I hope you all enjoyed what you've seen so far.

1375
01:23:21,000 --> 01:23:29,000
It's been pretty exciting for us here as well, as you guys have been inspired already just watching things and already cooking a new ascendancy class.

1376
01:23:30,000 --> 01:23:31,000
Yeah, for sure.

1377
01:23:32,000 --> 01:23:34,000
You've got to do design whenever you can.

1378
01:23:35,000 --> 01:23:36,000
Absolutely.

1379
01:23:36,000 --> 01:23:38,000
There's been a few fun moments here already.

1380
01:23:38,000 --> 01:23:43,000
But I'm your host, Ziggy D, and I'm joined by Jonathan and Mark to talk about everything you've seen.

1381
01:23:44,000 --> 01:23:45,000
Honestly, it's so much.

1382
01:23:46,000 --> 01:23:54,000
I mean, we were really keen to make sure that when we went into Early Access that people didn't feel like it was just, you know, limping along and kind of, you know, just like a minimal amount of content.

1383
01:23:54,000 --> 01:23:55,000
We really wanted to kind of blow people away.

1384
01:23:55,000 --> 01:23:58,000
So hopefully people feel like, yeah, there is enough content.

1385
01:23:58,000 --> 01:24:03,000
Because, yeah, it was certainly a mission to get all that stuff in.

1386
01:24:03,000 --> 01:24:12,000
Yeah, I did come here expecting that there would be, you know, maybe a basic mapping placeholder endgame and your three acts and, you know, the half the classes.

1387
01:24:12,000 --> 01:24:18,000
But you've made a decision here, clearly, that's got to go to the core POE player community in mind.

1388
01:24:18,000 --> 01:24:19,000
Absolutely.

1389
01:24:19,000 --> 01:24:20,000
So, I mean, we have to make sure.

1390
01:24:20,000 --> 01:24:28,000
Like, I mean, look, Path of Exile's endgame is kind of known for the fact that you get to choose between different types of content and that, like, you know, some people enjoy one thing, some people enjoy another.

1391
01:24:28,000 --> 01:24:31,000
And I feel like that choice is like a huge part of what makes it good.

1392
01:24:31,000 --> 01:24:36,000
So if we didn't have that when we entered endgame, then I don't think that would be, you know, like, that wouldn't be a Path of Exile endgame.

1393
01:24:37,000 --> 01:24:39,000
So that's kind of what we have to make sure of.

1394
01:24:39,000 --> 01:24:49,000
So we kind of said, okay, well, like, what is the minimum number of, like, different endgame things you need to be able to have in order to be able to actually have a viable endgame that you feel like you get different choices?

1395
01:24:49,000 --> 01:24:51,000
And that's how we ended up with what we have here.

1396
01:24:51,000 --> 01:24:58,000
I definitely feel like a lot of games nowadays release, you know, and their campaigns intact real good.

1397
01:24:58,000 --> 01:25:00,000
You get to the endgame and it just falls real flat.

1398
01:25:00,000 --> 01:25:01,000
Yeah.

1399
01:25:01,000 --> 01:25:07,000
And it was certainly a very important moment for us when we were like, hold on, that's the wrong thing to do.

1400
01:25:07,000 --> 01:25:09,000
Like, let's not make the same mistake as everyone else.

1401
01:25:09,000 --> 01:25:10,000
Let's pivot.

1402
01:25:10,000 --> 01:25:11,000
And we actually did that.

1403
01:25:11,000 --> 01:25:19,000
And like, it made a world of difference and made the game all of a sudden, you know, a hundred times bigger with an infinite amount more content.

1404
01:25:19,000 --> 01:25:20,000
Right.

1405
01:25:20,000 --> 01:25:23,000
It was definitely hard, though, because like, okay, like, so we're, you know, we're progressing.

1406
01:25:23,000 --> 01:25:25,000
It's like we would have, we would have made it.

1407
01:25:25,000 --> 01:25:28,000
We would have gotten, you know, all these acts in if we hadn't have changed direction.

1408
01:25:28,000 --> 01:25:32,000
It's like to actually say, you know what, we're going to specifically not finish this content.

1409
01:25:32,000 --> 01:25:36,000
We'll be working on, you know, that we, that we, that we, you know, it's like pins down everyone.

1410
01:25:36,000 --> 01:25:37,000
We're stopping work on this.

1411
01:25:37,000 --> 01:25:38,000
We're going to move over to end games.

1412
